            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>A cool demo I saw on Threads, showcasing this nice chunky rounded matte glass jelly effect.
I don't know how else to describe it. <a href="https://my.spline.design/glassmorphcursortracking-2ef6d3790000fd1a4f81c92fb3ff5bf5/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Link</a></p>
<p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" alt="Screenshot of glassmorphism demo with cursor tracking" src="https://bytehala.com/assets/images/spline-glassmorphism-c782204aa3931fa0a7174f35c1706d6a.png" width="2488" height="2382" class="img_ev3q"></p>
<p>I initially thought it was pure CSS. Turns out, it's a whole 3d "runtime".</p>
